-- Dana Gas of UAE Aims to Announce 30% Egypt Stake Sale This Year, CEO Says
-- B y   A n t h o n y   D i P a o l a
-- 2010-11-10T05:28:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/dana-gas-of-uae-aims-to-announce-30-egypt-stake-sale-this-year-ceo-says.html
Dana Gas PJSC, a United Arab
Emirates energy company, aims to announce the sale of as much as
30 percent in its Egyptian unit this year, Chief Executive
Officer Ahmed Al-Arbeed said in an interview today.  The company is in talks with potential buyers over the
transaction and is narrowing the bids down to arrive at the best
offer, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
